[b]CoilForge Zones v1.1[/b]

[b]What it does[/b]
CoilForge Zones identifies price compression phases — periods where the market coils before its next move — by combining five independent conditions into a single quality score. When a valid compression zone ends, the indicator stays armed for a configurable watch window and fires a confirmed breakout signal only when price exits with volume and rising ADX.

[b]Compression Scoring[/b]
[list]
[*][b]ATR Compression[/b] — range relative to ATR measures how tight the current window is (up to 25 pts, scales linearly)
[*][b]ADX Chop Filter[/b] — low ADX confirms the market is not in a trending phase (up to 15 pts, scales linearly)
[*][b]Volume Dry-Up[/b] — both the short and full volume windows sit below the moving average (15 pts)
[*][b]Impulse-In Context[/b] — a directional move before the zone confirms preceding momentum (15 pts)
[*][b]Historical S/R Reuse[/b] — the zone boundary aligns with a prior pivot level, adding structural confluence (10 pts)
[/list]

[b]Sensitivity Presets[/b]
[list]
[*][b]Strict[/b] — narrow range threshold, lower ADX limit, higher minimum score
[*][b]Balanced[/b] — default settings for most markets and timeframes
[*][b]Aggressive[/b] — wider tolerances for markets with higher baseline volatility
[*][b]Custom[/b] — full manual control over all thresholds
[/list]

[b]Post-Zone Breakout Detection[/b]
[list]
[*]Zone is armed for up to N bars after it closes (configurable)
[*]Breakout fires only when: close crosses the zone boundary + volume above MA + ADX rising
[*]Armed state expires automatically if no breakout occurs within the watch window
[*]Old zone boxes remain on the chart with a configurable lifetime for visual reference
[/list]

[b]Zone Bias[/b]
[list]
[*]Counts how many bars tested the upper vs. lower boundary within the zone
[*]Combined with DI direction and prior impulse, classifies as: Up, Down, Up/Continuation, Down/Continuation, or Neutral
[*]Zone box border color reflects the current bias (green = up pressure, red = down pressure)
[/list]

[b]Visuals[/b]
[list]
[*]Active zone box — color intensity driven by quality score, border by bias
[*]Floating label with score, bias, touch counts, and S/R reuse status
[*]Old zones fade to the background with configurable lifetime and maximum count
[*]Breakout markers: BO↑ / BO↓ plotted at the breakout bar
[*]Info table (top-right) with live zone state, score, bias, and breakout watch status
[/list]

[b]Alerts[/b]
All alerts fire only on confirmed bar close by default (configurable via "Alerts only on bar close" toggle).
[list]
[*][b]CoilForge Breakout Up[/b] — confirmed breakout above a coil zone
[*][b]CoilForge Breakout Down[/b] — confirmed breakout below a coil zone
[/list]

